				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
							<ul>
<li>KRs are Outcomes</li>
<li>Define what success looks like</li>
<li>Make them numerical</li>
<li>Use a scale that can be measured in real time (or as close as possible)</li>
<li>Avoid binary KRs</li>
<li>Avoid actions. If you can achieve it directly, it’s not a KR.</li>
<li>Include the initial value of the metric when describing the KR e.g. “Decrease defects in the field from 100 to 10”</li>
</ul>						</div>
